data.title: Prime Video: The Office UK
data.meta_description: A dysfunctional paper company in the heart of middle England, David Brent is a lower-middle-ranking manager in charge of a lower-middle-ranking office.
data.text:
David Brent, the manager of the Slough branch of Wernham Hogg paper company has a special visitor this morning, his boss, Jennifer Taylor-Clark. And Jennifer drops a piece of bad news for David and his branch when she reveals that either one of Swindon or Slough branch is to be merged with each other. Watch all the hilarity that ensues following the news, on Voot Select!

Gareth showcases his self-proclaimed 'extraordinary' ability to catch a culprit that created a vile doctored image of the new hiree, Donna. Watch this episode of The Office UK, now on Voot Select!

On Tim's 30th birthday, Dawn gifts him a sweet card, but it's an inflatable gift from Lee that steals the limelight. Catch this hilarious episode of The Office, now on Voot Select!

Tim finds a crack in the hole in Dawn and Lee's relationship when the couple's engagement hits a roadblock. And the staff undergoes a Training Day in this hilarious episode of The Office, now on Voot Select!

A frustrated Tim makes up his mind of going to a university to take up psychology, as selling papers do not seem to have a future. Rumours are spread around the workspace of Donna spending a night with someone from work. Who could that be?
